.Dd July 25, 2011
.Dt LGUE 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm lgue
.Nd USB CDC ethernet
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "device uhci"
.Cd "device ohci"
.Cd "device oldusb"
.Cd "device lgue"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for USB CDC (communication device class) ethernet.
It currently supports the
.Tn LG P-500
smartphone.
.Pp
For more information on configuring this device, see
.Xr ifconfig 8 .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr arp 4 ,
.Xr netintro 4 ,
.Xr ng_ether 4 ,
.Xr ifconfig 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver first appeared in
.Dx 2.11 .
